1
00:00:48,040 --> 00:00:49,640
Yunyuan, what are you doing?

2
00:00:50,880 --> 00:00:51,680
Yunyuan.

3
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:04,760
Oh, dear.

4
00:01:04,959 --> 00:01:06,160
What should we do?

5
00:01:06,240 --> 00:01:07,000
It looks like

6
00:01:07,320 --> 00:01:08,960
it's the backlash of the dark energy.

7
00:01:08,960 --> 00:01:10,560
Think of something, quick!

8
00:01:10,680 --> 00:01:12,039
The barrier the General set up...

9
00:01:12,039 --> 00:01:13,300
none of us can break it.

10
00:01:13,960 --> 00:01:15,760
We can only wait for him to come out on his own.

11
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:16,320
Di Yun.

12
00:01:16,600 --> 00:01:17,640
He's strong.

13
00:01:17,640 --> 00:01:19,720
Maybe the three of us can give it a try.

14
00:01:19,880 --> 00:01:21,340
I'll go find him right now.

15
00:01:39,840 --> 00:01:40,759
You're awake.

16
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:46,120
I prepared

17
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:48,000
your favorite Eight Treasure Porridge.

18
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:48,640
Yunyuan.

19
00:01:49,160 --> 00:01:50,880
I've never liked Eight Treasure Porridge.

20
00:01:50,880 --> 00:01:51,680
You're lying.

21
00:01:52,520 --> 00:01:54,039
You once told me

22
00:01:54,759 --> 00:01:56,960
you loved the Hailing Rice in it.

23
00:01:57,440 --> 00:01:59,520
You said it was chewy and fun to eat.

24
00:01:59,960 --> 00:02:01,120
Have you forgotten?

25
00:02:01,720 --> 00:02:03,560
He seems to be agitated.

26
00:02:03,640 --> 00:02:05,080
His emotions are unstable.

27
00:02:05,080 --> 00:02:06,280
I'll play along for now.

28
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:07,840
And find a way to escape later.

29
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:08,639
Yes.

30
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,320
I like it.

31
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:11,560
But like this,

32
00:02:12,040 --> 00:02:12,960
how can I eat?

33
00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:14,360
I'll feed you.

34
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:28,800
Yunyuan.

35
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:31,160
I'm full.

36
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:34,530
Yunyuan.

37
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:35,970
Why don't you

38
00:02:36,320 --> 00:02:37,840
untie me?

39
00:02:38,040 --> 00:02:39,320
I'm uncomfortable.

40
00:02:39,920 --> 00:02:40,780
I want to sleep.

41
00:02:41,440 --> 00:02:42,960
Are you going to stay here?

42
00:02:43,760 --> 00:02:45,480
If you keep staring at me like that,

43
00:02:45,480 --> 00:02:46,760
how can I sleep?

44
00:02:52,640 --> 00:02:53,440
Okay.

45
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:54,900
I won't look at you.

46
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:56,360
Go to sleep.

47
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:58,240
I'm certain now.

48
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:59,970
You have someone in your heart.

49
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:02,360
Someone who looks very much like me.

50
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:04,120
You're projecting all your love for her

51
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:05,560
onto me.

52
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:07,040
King Kunmi.

53
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,420
You are high above,

54
00:03:08,440 --> 00:03:09,440
out of reach.

55
00:03:09,880 --> 00:03:11,610
I'll just pretend I was bitten.

56
00:03:11,880 --> 00:03:12,760
Once I escape,

57
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:14,930
I'll stay far away from you.

58
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:16,450
And never see you again.

59
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:19,810
I have waited a thousand years for you.

60
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:21,079
It was so hard

61
00:03:21,760 --> 00:03:23,520
to have you back by my side.

62
00:03:27,760 --> 00:03:29,160
The Ling'er you speak of,

63
00:03:31,160 --> 00:03:31,760
is that me?

64
00:03:33,880 --> 00:03:35,140
The Ling'er I speak of,

65
00:03:36,079 --> 00:03:37,520
how could it not be you?

66
00:03:39,320 --> 00:03:40,760
It has always been you.

67
00:03:41,760 --> 00:03:43,079
It was you all along.

68
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:45,600
I just don't know why

69
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:48,120
you seem to have forgotten

70
00:03:48,120 --> 00:03:50,160
everything we shared.

71
00:03:56,640 --> 00:03:57,440
Di Yun.

72
00:03:57,880 --> 00:03:59,040
How is your injury?

73
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:01,360
I'm fine. Where is Ling'er?

74
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:02,560
How has she been lately?

75
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:03,760
My sworn brother took Ling'er away.

76
00:04:03,760 --> 00:04:04,960
I can't see her at all.

77
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:06,360
I told you before,

78
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:07,960
your sworn brother's mood was off.

79
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:09,160
He's losing his mind now,

80
00:04:09,160 --> 00:04:10,480
and is in danger of falling to the dark side at any moment.

81
00:04:10,480 --> 00:04:11,740
How could this happen?

82
00:04:12,440 --> 00:04:14,360
Whoever tied the bell must untie it.

83
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:15,960
Why is your sworn brother obsessed with Ling'er?

84
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:17,440
Shouldn't it be the Dragon Princess?

85
00:04:17,440 --> 00:04:19,240
Ling'er is the Dragon Princess.

86
00:04:19,440 --> 00:04:20,240
What?

87
00:04:20,959 --> 00:04:22,760
Ling'er is the Dragon Princess.

88
00:04:25,760 --> 00:04:27,080
So it was me...

89
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:29,200
I pushed Ling'er to Yunyuan with my own hands.

90
00:04:29,200 --> 00:04:31,640
Stop thinking about your ridiculous past from a thousand years ago.

91
00:04:31,640 --> 00:04:34,240
Think about how to help my sworn brother first.

92
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:35,560
You once said,

93
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:37,560
your sworn brother has been purifying demonic energy for a thousand years without issue.

94
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:39,159
Why would something happen at this critical moment?

95
00:04:39,159 --> 00:04:40,120
Think carefully.

96
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:42,180
Has he been acting strangely lately?

97
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:43,400
Strangely...

98
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:45,960
Even when you were pestering Ling'er before,

99
00:04:45,960 --> 00:04:47,680
my sworn brother just got angry.

100
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:49,040
He didn't lose control.

101
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:52,040
It seems that after Yinfeng showed up,

102
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:53,960
my sworn brother's emotions became more and more unstable.

103
00:04:53,960 --> 00:04:54,840
Yinfeng.

104
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:56,409
I always thought

105
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:59,330
he was just a petty demon who couldn't make waves.

106
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:01,320
What has he been doing lately?

107
00:05:01,320 --> 00:05:03,520
It seems after my sworn brother went mad,

108
00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:05,250
I haven't seen that brat since.

109
00:05:05,960 --> 00:05:07,080
All these incidents,

110
00:05:07,080 --> 00:05:08,160
when piled up together,

111
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:09,160
don't look right.

112
00:05:09,840 --> 00:05:11,280
I'm afraid Yunyuan fell into his trap.

113
00:05:11,280 --> 00:05:12,040
No way.

114
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:14,080
My sworn brother has powerful spiritual power.

115
00:05:14,080 --> 00:05:15,560
Yinfeng is just a petty demon.

116
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:17,360
How could he plot against my sworn brother?

117
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:18,840
What if it was a calculated plot against an unsuspecting victim?

118
00:05:18,840 --> 00:05:19,800
What if someone knew

119
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:20,880
Yunyuan used this method

120
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:22,160
to purify demonic energy,

121
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:24,200
and deliberately drove a large number of monsters here,

122
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:26,600
causing Yunyuan's body to be overwhelmed?

123
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:30,040
Come to think of it,

124
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:32,280
that actually makes sense.

125
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:34,740
I'll go kill that brat Yinfeng right now.

126
00:05:34,760 --> 00:05:35,690
Calm down first.

127
00:05:36,159 --> 00:05:37,290
The top priority now

128
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:39,080
is to find a way to bring Yunyuan back to his senses

129
00:05:39,080 --> 00:05:40,480
and then rescue Ling'er.

130
00:05:41,560 --> 00:05:43,159
This is a protective item my mother gave me.

131
00:05:43,159 --> 00:05:44,480
It can focus the mind and clear the heart.

132
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:45,159
Find a chance

133
00:05:45,159 --> 00:05:46,760
to give this to Yunyuan

134
00:05:46,840 --> 00:05:47,970
and make him wear it.

135
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:04,520
King of Kunmi.

136
00:06:05,640 --> 00:06:07,960
Let's see how long you can hold on.

137
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:20,640
When on earth will you let me go?

138
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:22,090
Except for that,

139
00:06:22,960 --> 00:06:24,800
I can agree to anything.

140
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:28,640
Ling'er.

141
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:30,400
Can you hear me?

142
00:06:30,520 --> 00:06:31,360
Ling'er!

143
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:32,320
Get out!

144
00:06:35,960 --> 00:06:36,760
Yunyuan!

145
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:42,080
Is it working?

146
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:47,240
I can't believe I can't break his barrier.

147
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:47,680
You...

148
00:06:47,960 --> 00:06:50,159
If you keep this up, they'll be worried.

149
00:06:50,159 --> 00:06:51,320
How about I go find them,

150
00:06:51,320 --> 00:06:52,360
tell them what's happening,

151
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:53,800
and tell them not to worry.

152
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:54,240
Sure.

153
00:07:02,480 --> 00:07:03,280
But,

154
00:07:06,320 --> 00:07:07,560
I'm coming with you.

155
00:07:07,760 --> 00:07:08,160
You...

156
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:09,890
How can you be like this?

157
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:18,560
Oh, my.

158
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:21,200
You finally decided to come out.

159
00:07:21,200 --> 00:07:23,080
If I knew you two wanted some alone time,

160
00:07:23,080 --> 00:07:25,880
I wouldn't have rushed over to save you.

161
00:07:26,280 --> 00:07:28,080
Don't provoke my sworn brother.

162
00:07:29,320 --> 00:07:29,850
Ling'er,

163
00:07:29,960 --> 00:07:30,920
are you alright?

164
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:33,680
Brother.

165
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:35,600
This is really inappropriate.

166
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:37,800
I know you care deeply about my sister-in-law,

167
00:07:37,800 --> 00:07:40,360
but there are others present.

168
00:07:42,440 --> 00:07:43,360
Hey, Yunyuan.

169
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:44,659
That's enough.

170
00:07:45,159 --> 00:07:46,520
Once you're done messing around,

171
00:07:46,520 --> 00:07:47,850
come out and get to work.

172
00:07:55,159 --> 00:07:56,420
You guys go back first.

173
00:07:56,840 --> 00:07:58,560
Ling'er and I will be right there.

174
00:07:58,560 --> 00:07:59,600
You said it.

175
00:08:00,400 --> 00:08:02,060
We'll wait for you back there.

176
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:03,200
Hurry up.

177
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:04,920
You're the King of Kunmi, after all.

178
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:05,720
Don't be so irresponsible.

179
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:06,440
Let's go.

180
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:13,160
You did that on purpose.

181
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:13,960
Yes.

182
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:16,120
I did it on purpose.

183
00:08:16,960 --> 00:08:18,680
I wanted them to know

184
00:08:20,080 --> 00:08:21,720
that you're mine now.

185
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:25,400
Just play along with him for now.

186
00:08:25,400 --> 00:08:26,860
Escape first, talk later.

187
00:08:27,640 --> 00:08:29,440
How long are you going to hold me?

188
00:08:32,799 --> 00:08:33,200
Hey!

189
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:35,490
Didn't you promise them you'd go back?

190
00:08:37,159 --> 00:08:37,880
Yunyuan!

191
00:08:38,280 --> 00:08:39,120
You bastard!

192
00:08:42,120 --> 00:08:44,120
I should have been a bastard sooner.

193
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:45,560
A thousand years ago,

194
00:08:45,920 --> 00:08:48,960
I should have abandoned all that restraint and propriety.

195
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:49,760
Shameless!

196
00:08:49,760 --> 00:08:50,480
Hooligan!

197
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:51,160
Pervert!

198
00:09:00,240 --> 00:09:01,640
It seems like for a while,

199
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:03,180
those two won't be coming.

200
00:09:05,680 --> 00:09:07,160
Drink some tea.

201
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:09,900
This is already the third cup.

202
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:26,680
Brother.

203
00:09:31,400 --> 00:09:32,400
Where is Ling'er?

204
00:09:34,280 --> 00:09:35,520
Resting in my room.

205
00:09:37,560 --> 00:09:38,200
Brother,

206
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:40,000
have you felt recently

207
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:41,760
that the dark energy inside you is only increasing?

208
00:09:41,760 --> 00:09:42,440
Indeed.

209
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:49,090
It seems our guess was correct.

210
00:09:49,160 --> 00:09:50,760
Someone is deliberately driving

211
00:09:50,760 --> 00:09:52,280
demons heavy with dark energy toward Kunmi

212
00:09:52,280 --> 00:09:53,400
to affect you.

213
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:55,040
Take this jade pendant.

214
00:09:55,040 --> 00:09:56,560
Keep it with you at all times.

215
00:09:56,560 --> 00:09:58,090
It can stabilize your mind.

216
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:02,280
Thank you.

217
00:10:03,040 --> 00:10:04,040
I just don't know,

218
00:10:04,160 --> 00:10:05,240
in doing this,

219
00:10:05,520 --> 00:10:06,580
what their goal is.

220
00:10:06,760 --> 00:10:08,160
If I'm not mistaken,

221
00:10:08,560 --> 00:10:11,240
it must be for the Spirit Pearl Ling'er possesses.

222
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:11,880
Yunyuan,

223
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:13,780
you really are something.

224
00:10:13,920 --> 00:10:15,560
You know full well Ling'er is my fiancée, yet...

225
00:10:15,560 --> 00:10:16,960
If I remember correctly,

226
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:21,010
you went to great lengths to break off the engagement back then.

227
00:10:21,800 --> 00:10:23,240
Seeing that you are injured,

228
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:24,560
I won't hold it against you.

229
00:10:24,560 --> 00:10:25,760
A defeated opponent.

230
00:10:26,040 --> 00:10:28,040
It is I who won't hold it against you.

231
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:30,160
Aren't you afraid I'll return to the Heavenly Clan

232
00:10:30,160 --> 00:10:32,360
and ask the Emperor to fulfill the engagement?

233
00:10:32,360 --> 00:10:33,420
You wouldn't dare.

234
00:10:34,480 --> 00:10:35,040
Brother,

235
00:10:35,480 --> 00:10:36,560
don't be angry.

236
00:10:37,360 --> 00:10:38,040
Diyun,

237
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:39,580
don't provoke my brother.

238
00:10:40,440 --> 00:10:41,200
Enough.

239
00:10:41,800 --> 00:10:43,120
I was just saying.

240
00:10:45,640 --> 00:10:46,560
Look at you.

241
00:10:47,160 --> 00:10:47,640
Well?

242
00:10:48,160 --> 00:10:48,920
What's next?

243
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:50,130
What are your plans?

244
00:10:51,680 --> 00:10:53,160
This is a matter for Kunmi.

245
00:10:53,800 --> 00:10:54,730
What is it to you?

246
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:56,080
What is it to me?

247
00:10:56,680 --> 00:10:58,280
If not for Ling'er's sake,

248
00:10:58,400 --> 00:10:59,560
whether you fall to the demonic path

249
00:10:59,560 --> 00:11:01,000
or destroy your primordial spirit,

250
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:02,160
what would it matter to me?

251
00:11:02,160 --> 00:11:03,360
I know what I'm doing.

252
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:04,880
Stay out of it.

253
00:11:06,000 --> 00:11:07,560
This concerns the Three Realms.

254
00:11:07,560 --> 00:11:09,160
I am making this my business.

255
00:11:11,640 --> 00:11:13,200
Did you think of something?

256
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:15,600
I remember a thousand years ago,

257
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:17,400
the Spirit Pearl was shattered.

258
00:11:17,800 --> 00:11:19,840
But the Spirit Pearl Ling'er took out that day

259
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:21,240
seemed to have no issues.

260
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:23,420
The Spirit Pearl was indeed damaged.

261
00:11:24,040 --> 00:11:24,880
However,

262
00:11:25,560 --> 00:11:26,840
I braved countless dangers

263
00:11:26,840 --> 00:11:28,360
to find the Qiankun Cauldron

264
00:11:28,360 --> 00:11:30,280
and barely managed to repair the Spirit Pearl.

265
00:11:30,280 --> 00:11:32,760
Compared to your thousand years of guardianship and sacrifice,

266
00:11:32,760 --> 00:11:34,090
I have lost completely.

267
00:11:36,240 --> 00:11:38,000
Since the Spirit Pearl is repaired,

268
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:39,800
why do you say there is a problem?

269
00:11:39,880 --> 00:11:41,200
The pearl itself is repaired,

270
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:44,000
but the pearl soul was severely damaged back then.

271
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:46,680
I placed the pearl soul in the Qiankun Cauldron to nurture it.

272
00:11:46,680 --> 00:11:49,480
The current Spirit Pearl is merely a hollow shell.

273
00:11:49,640 --> 00:11:50,840
I see.

274
00:11:51,160 --> 00:11:51,890
Then for now,

275
00:11:52,120 --> 00:11:53,680
let's have Ling'er stay indoors.

276
00:11:53,680 --> 00:11:54,560
What about Yinfeng?

277
00:11:54,560 --> 00:11:55,680
Don't worry about him.

278
00:11:55,680 --> 00:11:56,760
What he needs to know,

279
00:11:56,760 --> 00:11:58,160
he already knows.

280
00:11:58,200 --> 00:12:00,160
I deliberately released false information,

281
00:12:00,160 --> 00:12:02,160
so he wouldn't easily harm Ling'er.

282
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:04,960
You drew all the attention to yourself

283
00:12:05,400 --> 00:12:06,960
to prevent them from hurting Ling'er.

284
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:08,220
None of your business.

285
00:12:08,760 --> 00:12:09,960
You can leave now.

286
00:12:10,360 --> 00:12:11,760
You don't need to chase me away.

287
00:12:11,760 --> 00:12:13,160
If it weren't for Ling'er,

288
00:12:13,160 --> 00:12:14,520
a place like Cloud Recesses...

289
00:12:14,520 --> 00:12:15,560
I wouldn't even care for it.

290
00:12:15,560 --> 00:12:16,600
I'll say it again.

291
00:12:17,360 --> 00:12:18,680
Unless you two get married,

292
00:12:18,680 --> 00:12:19,940
I will never back down.

293
00:12:20,400 --> 00:12:21,080
After all,

294
00:12:21,560 --> 00:12:23,620
my engagement to Ling'er came first.

295
00:12:24,040 --> 00:12:26,240
Sooner or later, I'll win Ling'er back.

296
00:12:30,680 --> 00:12:32,080
What a graceless fellow.

297
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:33,770
When you've recovered,

298
00:12:33,800 --> 00:12:35,560
I'll fight you properly.

299
00:12:35,880 --> 00:12:37,410
I won't bother with you now.

300
00:12:40,880 --> 00:12:42,880
I never considered you an opponent.

301
00:12:43,960 --> 00:12:45,880
Why humiliate yourself?

302
00:12:49,640 --> 00:12:50,970
Diyun, I'll see you out.

303
00:13:06,160 --> 00:13:06,680
Shihun.

304
00:13:06,840 --> 00:13:08,440
Greetings, Great Guardian.

305
00:13:09,200 --> 00:13:10,120
Great Guardian,

306
00:13:10,120 --> 00:13:10,920
we found it.

307
00:13:12,520 --> 00:13:14,400
We found the soul of the Spirit Bead.

308
00:13:14,400 --> 00:13:16,200
Not only did I find the soul of the Spirit Bead,

309
00:13:16,200 --> 00:13:17,760
but I also found the Qiankun Cauldron.

310
00:13:17,760 --> 00:13:20,020
The Qiankun Cauldron has been found too.

311
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:21,800
My Lord.

312
00:13:22,840 --> 00:13:24,170
Greetings, Demon Lord.

313
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:25,320
Reporting to the Demon Lord.

314
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:26,960
I have found the Qiankun Cauldron.

315
00:13:26,960 --> 00:13:28,690
It is in the hands of King Kunmi.

316
00:13:28,840 --> 00:13:29,760
King Kunmi?

317
00:13:30,520 --> 00:13:33,120
It seems the Cauldron has recognized a master.

318
00:13:33,280 --> 00:13:35,120
The soul of the Spirit Bead is inside the Cauldron.

319
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:35,920
However,

320
00:13:36,040 --> 00:13:37,480
it seems to be recuperating.

321
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:39,480
King Kunmi is an overly cautious man.

322
00:13:39,480 --> 00:13:41,200
I dared not get too close.

323
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:42,160
Good.

324
00:13:42,160 --> 00:13:45,080
(Laughs)

325
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:48,160
He is just a naive child after all.

326
00:13:48,720 --> 00:13:52,600
Let him restore the Bead's soul for me.

327
00:13:53,680 --> 00:13:55,040
Keep watching them.

328
00:13:55,880 --> 00:13:58,120
Take no action for now.

329
00:14:00,120 --> 00:14:01,050
Great Guardian.

330
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:03,040
The Demon Lord means,

331
00:14:03,840 --> 00:14:04,900
for the time being,

332
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:06,560
you stay in the Demon Realm.

333
00:14:07,320 --> 00:14:08,960
The day we see the light again

334
00:14:09,360 --> 00:14:10,400
is not far off.

335
00:14:11,280 --> 00:14:12,480
When that time comes,

336
00:14:12,680 --> 00:14:14,160
the whole world

337
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:17,880
will belong to the Demon Clan.

338
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:23,360
Three hundred miles west of the city. Eliminate the Shadow Demon.

339
00:14:23,360 --> 00:14:26,360
Twin Pagoda Temple. Illusion Demon causing trouble.

340
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:29,080
Why are they all from the Demon Clan?

341
00:14:29,840 --> 00:14:30,840
Sister Qingluan.

342
00:14:34,600 --> 00:14:35,800
Ling'er, you're here.

343
00:14:35,800 --> 00:14:36,800
Sister Qingluan,

344
00:14:37,560 --> 00:14:38,960
I want to ask you,

345
00:14:39,560 --> 00:14:42,490
what is the Dragon Princess in Yunyuan's heart like?

346
00:14:43,040 --> 00:14:44,240
The Dragon Princess?

347
00:14:44,240 --> 00:14:45,900
Ling'er, do you remember now?

348
00:14:46,040 --> 00:14:46,720
Sister Qingluan,

349
00:14:46,720 --> 00:14:48,250
what are you talking about?

350
00:14:48,800 --> 00:14:49,660
You don't know?

351
00:14:50,400 --> 00:14:52,960
The Dragon Princess my sworn brother has guarded for a thousand years

352
00:14:52,960 --> 00:14:54,160
is you.

353
00:14:54,360 --> 00:14:55,760
I am the Dragon Princess?

354
00:14:55,760 --> 00:14:56,280
Yes.

355
00:14:57,840 --> 00:14:59,700
A young boy bullied by evil demons

356
00:14:59,840 --> 00:15:01,360
met the Dragon Princess.

357
00:15:01,720 --> 00:15:04,240
The kind little princess saved the boy.

358
00:15:04,800 --> 00:15:06,200
The boy cultivated hard.

359
00:15:06,360 --> 00:15:07,720
He fought his way up,

360
00:15:08,240 --> 00:15:09,640
from an unknown soldier

361
00:15:09,960 --> 00:15:11,960
to a distinguished young general.

362
00:15:12,320 --> 00:15:13,560
The boy thought

363
00:15:13,840 --> 00:15:15,560
that with his years of effort,

364
00:15:15,960 --> 00:15:18,560
he could be worthy of the princess in his heart.

365
00:15:18,600 --> 00:15:20,200
But a marriage contract

366
00:15:20,440 --> 00:15:21,920
severed his chance at love.

367
00:15:21,920 --> 00:15:22,760
Fortunately,

368
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:24,160
the other party

369
00:15:24,160 --> 00:15:25,720
ended the engagement herself.

370
00:15:25,720 --> 00:15:26,720
So the boy

371
00:15:26,720 --> 00:15:28,000
summoned his courage

372
00:15:28,560 --> 00:15:30,760
and confessed his love to the princess.

373
00:15:31,120 --> 00:15:32,440
They fell in love.

374
00:15:33,160 --> 00:15:34,120
However,

375
00:15:34,440 --> 00:15:36,480
before they could discuss marriage,

376
00:15:36,480 --> 00:15:38,410
a disaster struck the Dragon Clan.

377
00:15:38,600 --> 00:15:41,200
The princess sacrificed herself to protect her clan

378
00:15:41,200 --> 00:15:42,800
and fell into a deep slumber.

379
00:15:43,240 --> 00:15:45,640
The young general overcame all obstacles,

380
00:15:46,160 --> 00:15:47,920
searched the ends of the earth,

381
00:15:48,560 --> 00:15:50,160
and obtained the Divine Cauldron.

382
00:15:50,160 --> 00:15:51,290
Nurturing the soul,

383
00:15:51,640 --> 00:15:53,200
for a promise to his beloved,

384
00:15:53,200 --> 00:15:54,760
saving the realm's people.

385
00:15:55,760 --> 00:15:58,000
Guarding faithfully for a thousand years.

386
00:15:58,000 --> 00:15:59,660
Waiting for a thousand years.

387
00:16:00,600 --> 00:16:02,060
Hearing all this from you,

388
00:16:03,840 --> 00:16:04,960
my heart aches.

389
00:16:08,440 --> 00:16:09,840
I can't control my tears.

390
00:16:11,240 --> 00:16:14,160
Even though I have no memory of what you said,

391
00:16:14,600 --> 00:16:17,960
I feel as if I experienced it all myself.

392
00:16:18,160 --> 00:16:19,800
My mind tells me

393
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:21,530
it has nothing to do with me.

394
00:16:23,560 --> 00:16:25,360
But my heart tells me,

395
00:16:27,440 --> 00:16:28,720
"Listen."

396
00:16:30,160 --> 00:16:32,280
"This is what he did for you."

397
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:34,220
"Every single thing,"

398
00:16:35,320 --> 00:16:36,520
"every single deed."

399
00:16:37,520 --> 00:16:39,580
Every word enters my ears in silence,

400
00:16:41,360 --> 00:16:43,160
yet brands itself onto my heart.

401
00:16:46,800 --> 00:16:47,840
Sister Qingluan.

402
00:16:48,440 --> 00:16:49,840
But why?

403
00:16:51,080 --> 00:16:54,040
Why can't I remember?

404
00:16:55,560 --> 00:16:56,360
Ling'er.

405
00:16:57,560 --> 00:16:58,840
You are you.

406
00:16:59,560 --> 00:17:01,020
Even if you've forgotten,

407
00:17:01,560 --> 00:17:02,960
my sworn brother hasn't.

408
00:17:04,960 --> 00:17:06,760
He carved you into his bones,

409
00:17:07,200 --> 00:17:08,960
engraved you in his heart.

410
00:17:09,119 --> 00:17:11,520
He gouged out his heart-protecting scale,

411
00:17:11,560 --> 00:17:13,819
just to protect your primordial spirit.

412
00:17:13,960 --> 00:17:15,290
He removed his own bone,

413
00:17:15,800 --> 00:17:17,660
to make the hairpin for your hair.

414
00:17:18,520 --> 00:17:20,000
He split part of his soul,

415
00:17:20,960 --> 00:17:22,619
so that when you are in danger,

416
00:17:23,760 --> 00:17:25,490
he could save you immediately.

417
00:17:26,040 --> 00:17:27,560
He gave his life to you.

418
00:17:29,040 --> 00:17:30,560
He loved you to the bone.

419
00:17:32,600 --> 00:17:34,080
Even if

420
00:17:34,280 --> 00:17:36,280
he ended up suffering Qi deviation.

421
00:17:36,520 --> 00:17:37,600
He suffered Qi deviation.
